ğŸ›¡ï¸ A. Sensor-Level Defenses

Defense Method	Effectiveness	Details

Optical Filters	âœ… Moderate	Blocks out specific wavelengths (e.g., IR >800nm). Can be dynamic (LC)
Polarization Filters	âš ï¸ Limited	Reduces glare, especially from visible light lasers
Photochromic Lenses	âœ… Moderate	Darkens in response to intense light, reducing exposure
Shutter Mechanisms	âœ…âœ… High	Fast electromechanical or LCD shutter blocks light overload instantly
